<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Six articles were promulgated and enacted on March 15, 2010 by the order of the National Communications Commission (NCC)]]></沿革內容>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These Standards are enacted pursuant to Article 70 of the Telecommunications Act and Article 50-1 of the Radio and Television Act by NCC.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The statutory fees include charges for inspection, examination, and the licensing of radio and TV station facilities. The charging items and tariffs are as attached.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The statutory fees shall be paid upon application for the inspection and examination of stations; and upon the issuing of licenses.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Applicants should remit the statutory fees in the form of cash, bank check, treasury check, or bank draft to NCC.
The aforementioned bank check, treasury check or bank draft should be made payable to NCC.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[With the exceptions of overpayments, mistaken payments, or the stipulation of any other law, payment shall not be returned to applicants.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards shall come into effect from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
